欺人、贻误发展的行为，一旦发现将从严从快处理、严肃追责问责、全省通报曝光，确保统计数据真实，确保经得起历史和人民检验。人民日报-有品质的新闻"},"attached_info":"Cj8I8KfA+tDG3IElEAMaCDgyNTYxMDIxIIf5g5YGMD84wAtAMXIJNTQxMjU1NTkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-250a528c5a0efaf1af043f4ed2be776c_1440w.png"}]}],"description":{"time":"2022-07-04 13:33:16"}}